item.title: By: Marlon Ribunal
item.dc:creator: Marlon Ribunal
item.description: The SQL Community is a tech community like no other! Indeed! The SQL Community is a very important part of my current journey! That is why I try to give back when opportunity presents itself (co-organize SQL Saturdays, volunteer, blog, etc). SQL Friends is another "expression" of the SQL Community that I'd love to attend if there is one in my area :-)
